  ## Authentication Test

  This request deliberately **omits the X-Emby-Token header**.

  **Expected Result:**
  - HTTP 401 Unauthorized or 403 Forbidden
  - Request should be rejected

  **Acceptance Criteria:**
  - ✅ All endpoints require admin authentication
  - ✅ Requests without token are rejected
  - ✅ Non-admin users are rejected (if you have a non-admin user to test)

  **To Test:**
  1. Run this request (no token) → should fail
  2. Add invalid token → should fail
  3. Add valid admin token → should succeed
}
